WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.054
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:00:20.055 --> 00:00:50.919
Your other screen don't work, but you have one screen. Let me know when people are here, son; I can't tell here.

00:00:50.920 --> 00:01:05.399
Is it good? Yeah, it's not. I'm saying seven. It's saying seven right now, but—well, good morning, good evening.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:12.079
Thank you for joining so quickly. We're waiting; we're having a lot of technical issues.

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:20.879
That's why I'm late. That's why I usually do not announce when I'm coming on here live.

00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:27.712
The enemy does not like this prayer time, obviously. And so, I'm not frustrated.

00:01:27.713 --> 00:01:34.794
I know that we're a threat. You know, it's exciting when you know you're poking them in the eye.

00:01:34.795 --> 00:01:45.319
But we've had a lot of stuff going on with all our internet and our cameras and everything else, so it's been a little bit of a hiccup here today.

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:49.999
So, is it working now? Everything's good? 800? Okay, good. Well, praise the Lord.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:56.534
Well, good afternoon, good evening, and good night, whatever, wherever you are in the world.

00:01:56.535 --> 00:02:00.609
Thank you for joining us again today. We're going to just take right off.

00:02:00.610 --> 00:02:09.917
I don't have a lot of time here now because I'm a little behind. So, I'm going to just get right into it and pray with y'all.

00:02:09.918 --> 00:02:28.610
Yesterday when we were praying, the glory of the Lord filled our hotel room, and it was—I told Braden, we all felt it—it was the peace that passes all understanding, just that weightiness of the presence of God filled this room.

00:02:28.611 --> 00:02:38.359
And I was surprised, honestly. I mean, you're in a hotel that's not your house and, you know, on the road like this, and the glory of the Lord shows up like that.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:48.489
I was just in awe at just the presence of the Lord, and it was just exciting that the Lord would visit like that.

00:02:48.490 --> 00:02:58.788
We've been at the prayer conference and praying over what they feel led to pray over concerning America and things like that.

00:02:58.789 --> 00:03:05.359
But my heart is going to tell you this: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:03:05.360 --> 00:03:18.105
You must know this. You must have an urgency about our Father's return. It is time that the body of Christ has urgency and wakes up.

00:03:18.106 --> 00:03:24.753
We are in the last of the last of the last seconds before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:03:24.754 --> 00:03:34.053
We see the wars and the rumors of wars. We see Israel and what's going on with Israel, watching the fig tree.

00:03:34.054 --> 00:03:45.159
But as we pray today, the enemy within—we'll just pick up where we left off yesterday with the terrorist attacks.

00:03:45.160 --> 00:03:58.999
I know what the Lord is showing me. They were picking up on some of it today concerning July the 4th of this year because it's an anniversary year.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:08.259
It's the big celebration. I think it's 200 and some years or whatever it is, the 250th for the United States of America.

00:04:08.260 --> 00:04:19.116
But what I'm picking up on is way before July of 2026. We must pray for our elections in 2026 for sure.

00:04:19.117 --> 00:04:27.593
This is a major hot spot for everything that I'm getting concerning November of next year.

00:04:27.594 --> 00:04:32.928
This time next year, I pray we've already prayed this thing through.

00:04:32.929 --> 00:04:37.876
We don't need to be coming up to the wire and praying it through; we need to tackle this thing now.

00:04:37.877 --> 00:04:50.459
The elections of 2026, if we do not keep the Senate and the House and get some better judges in our nation, it won't do any good to even have the presidency.

00:04:50.460 --> 00:05:03.239
We must keep the Senate with more of a majority and the House to push through some of the things that I have seen.

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:10.778
Now, I believe that we have—there's power in numbers, there's power in prayer. And it's so exciting to meet some of you all.

00:05:10.779 --> 00:05:16.968
I met some people from Sweden today, some from Mexico, and another man who just saw me.

00:05:16.969 --> 00:05:27.566
I said, "Are you here for the prayer conference?"He said, "No, I just came here for a vacation."You know, Branson, Missouri is a major hot spot for vacation for a lot of people.

00:05:27.567 --> 00:05:36.999
And Sister Billie said that today, that an average of 8 million people come through here every single year.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:43.918
And when I was driving around today, the Lord said, "I told you this."He said, "I'm getting it ready for the revival.

00:05:43.919 --> 00:05:49.013
Do you remember what I said?"I said, "Yes, Lord, you picked a good spot.

00:05:49.014 --> 00:06:15.406
8 million visitors a year."And she said, "That's more people that visit here than visit Israel."And I was like, "That's amazing for this little bitty town, that we have more visitors come here in this little area in Branson, Missouri than Israel has in all of the tourist season of Israel in a whole entire single year."That's amazing.

00:06:15.407 --> 00:06:23.653
So, it shows why the Lord picked Branson, Missouri for a major revival, because there's already all these people coming here.

00:06:23.654 --> 00:06:33.374
So, He picked a hot spot in America. He said, "I choose to pick the central part of America on the New Madrid fault.

00:06:33.375 --> 00:06:54.209
This is going to be a major place for a major shaking to awaken, and a great revival will come to Branson, Missouri."And as I was driving around today, the roads were so congested with so many people coming here for fall break, I just thought, you know, like Sister Billie always says, "Oh, what a plan.

00:06:54.210 --> 00:06:59.393
Oh, what a planner."And I'm telling you all, I have such high expectations.

00:06:59.394 --> 00:07:16.239
I can, as I'm in the exact spot where I've always seen the visions looking out over where the sun is setting, looking out and the Lord's saying, "Brandon, this dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:24.288
The ark door is closing. Jesus is coming."Do you understand, ladies and gentlemen? We're about to have the greatest harvest of souls.

00:07:24.289 --> 00:07:32.618
And I say that all the time, but I want to be that steady drum that keeps warning you about what's coming.

00:07:32.619 --> 00:07:39.879
So, we see Zelensky in the White House today asking for Tomahawks.

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:47.359
And I said, "This is not a coincidence."I saw this way before they are even talking about this, folks.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:51.658
And here President Trump—oh, and then Putin had the meeting there saying, "We need to talk about this.

00:07:51.659 --> 00:08:01.466
We don't want those long-range missiles coming into Moscow."And the reach was way beyond Moscow for what these missiles are able to do.

00:08:01.467 --> 00:08:14.128
But Zelensky was putting a demand on the relationship with the United States of America stating that he wanted long-range missiles to go way deep into Russia, and we don't want that.

00:08:14.129 --> 00:08:17.705
So, that's why we're praying, because I believe prayer changes things.

00:08:17.706 --> 00:08:31.998
But it is important that we realize that we are going to avert World War III in a great capacity in some areas.

00:08:31.999 --> 00:08:37.158
Now, can we stop the whole thing? No. But I believe we can stop some of it.

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:40.559
We can cause some peace in some of it, maybe delay some of it, I don't know.

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:44.483
But the Lord said some of this stuff is going to happen because His Word said it would.

00:08:44.484 --> 00:09:05.676
So, we see these things happening in the news and what they're talking about, and I'm like—I told Diana, I said, "You know what's amazing to me is whenever you're seeing it in prayer weeks before, and then you start seeing it in the news weeks after, right?"And you just go, "Wow, Lord.

00:09:05.677 --> 00:09:18.503
Wow. Wow. Nothing happens on this earth before He reveals it to His servants, the prophets, and I believe the watchmen of this generation."He said, "I'm bringing in my closers."And He keeps bringing that up to me.

00:09:18.504 --> 00:09:29.185
It's time for impartation. You know what was interesting? I felt to talk to one of the key head prayer people, Sister Lynne.

00:09:29.186 --> 00:09:38.562
And I told D, I said, "I feel I just would like her to pray for us because she's a general. She's been—she's taught us prayer our whole entire lives.

00:09:38.562 --> 00:09:52.054
I mean, since we were little kids walking around, you know, barely in diapers."And it was an honor that she would even talk to us, and she's excited because she says she watches our channel and stuff.

00:09:52.055 --> 00:10:00.606
And she laid hands on Diana. And I've never seen the power of God move on my wife like that other than when we've been at some Billy Burke meetings.

00:10:00.607 --> 00:10:09.079
But my wife's hand shook under the power of God, which I don't understand why, but it shook under the power of God.

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:22.882
Now, usually it's always the whole being—you can feel it and it goes in you—but her right hand, where Sister Lyn Hammond prayed for my wife and grabbed a hold of her hand, shook for over an hour and she couldn't control it.

00:10:22.883 --> 00:10:28.758
It was just under the power of God. Her whole arm was; she could feel it from her fingers all the way up to her shoulder.

00:10:28.759 --> 00:10:37.439
Come and tell them. You're sitting here. You tell them. I ain't going to steal her thunder.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:44.698
Here, you can sit on my lap. You want to sit right here? I don't have to—you told it really good.

00:10:44.699 --> 00:10:55.734
I know. Can you see her? All right. Tell them. Yeah. Whenever she laid hands on us and prayed, she put her hand right here on my arm.

00:10:55.735 --> 00:11:02.574
And when she did, I felt the power of God go into my arm. And it went all the way from here to my elbow.

00:11:02.575 --> 00:11:06.569
And it traveled. It kind of stopped right there, but it was all through my hand.

00:11:06.570 --> 00:11:11.592
And I just felt it vibrating like a vibration, like a current.

00:11:11.593 --> 00:11:22.039
And I was watching my hand, and I was like—she was praying and I was feeling it—and I was thinking, 'Wow, this is like my hand. I can feel the power of God.'And I was just weeping.

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:30.842
And then she put her hand up here on my shoulder, and I felt it come all the way down my arm clear to my elbow, and it went all the way up and down.

00:11:30.843 --> 00:11:36.959
My whole hand was just under the power for over an hour. It was like being electrocuted.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:41.475
Yes. And it really was amazing because I've never seen you do that.

00:11:41.476 --> 00:11:51.135
And even our littlest was like, 'Daddy, can Mommy control her hand?'Because Paisley was just staring at it, you know, because her mom's hand was sitting there just shaking.

00:11:51.136 --> 00:12:00.701
And it was just amazing to see that. I knew there was impartation—there's something, because that's just not normal for us.

00:12:00.702 --> 00:12:12.205
And we don't put on—we ain't here for a show. We don't care. You know, it's like to us, we're just Brandon and Diana, you know, and there's no performance.

00:12:12.206 --> 00:12:16.519
You get what you get. I'm not here to try to entertain you. And that's why I've always maintained that.

00:12:16.520 --> 00:12:24.521
Keep being authentic. No matter how much it gets bigger, don't try to be a performance.

00:12:24.522 --> 00:12:29.259
There is no time for performance. It's fake. I don't like fake Christianity.

00:12:29.260 --> 00:12:36.806
I don't like fake Holy Ghost stuff. No, I want the real, authentic move and touch of the power of God.

00:12:36.807 --> 00:12:42.695
And if it's not, I don't want it at all. I'm not here, you know. I see some people and you think, 'Is that real?

00:12:42.696 --> 00:12:58.508
Is that whatever?'And I don't try to judge them, but I'm saying there are a lot of times you realize that their flesh is involved more than the spirit, you know, and I'm just like, 'I don't want to be one of those.'But I realize when my wife is getting a touch from the Lord, and it's authentic, because Diana is a no-nonsense person.

00:12:58.509 --> 00:13:09.822
And so, it's the same with me. I'm a no-nonsense person. I don't play Holy Ghost.

00:13:09.823 --> 00:13:15.340
It's either real or it's not. And because I see, I don't give any courtesy falls.

00:13:15.341 --> 00:13:21.853
If the power of God's not there to knock me on my heinie, I don't want it, you know. I'll resist it more than anything.

00:13:21.854 --> 00:13:32.359
And so I just say, 'Hey,'because I'm not going to let you push me down, either—'Holy Ghost push.'You know, people try to push you down in the name of the power of God and try to make you go down, and you're like, 'No, that's not the power of God.

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:45.359
That's you knocking me down with your hand. Stop with your nonsense.'But I'm just saying, you know when the Lord is authentically touching somebody, and my wife got a touch today, and I was so thankful for that.

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:53.805
I told her, I said, 'We're Holy Ghost junkies. We're going to find the authentic.'And Sister Lynn touched Diana today, and it was pretty awesome.

00:13:53.806 --> 00:14:00.897
So I just wanted to tell you all that, you know. Love you, baby.

00:14:00.898 --> 00:14:05.248
So pretty cool. That's not you. Don't you understand what I'm saying?

00:14:05.249 --> 00:14:13.448
You get the anointing of push on you, and they ain't going to have the anointing of push, and they start going, and you go, 'That's not the anointing of the Holy Ghost.

00:14:13.449 --> 00:14:21.540
You're trying to push people down.'And they give you a courtesy fall because you're pushing their head off. But I just like, you know, I want authentic.

00:14:21.541 --> 00:14:31.608
And there has been something authentic in our life, and we've touched it and tasted it, and I'm telling you, the Holy Spirit is real, and it puts a bad taste in some people's mouths whenever it's not.

00:14:31.609 --> 00:14:36.901
Now, I get off on that because I come across people and they say, 'Well, is this real?

00:14:36.902 --> 00:14:48.743
Is it? Is it not?'And I'm telling you, it's real. When I've been prayed for by Billy Burke, you can't stand; the glory comes in.

00:14:48.744 --> 00:15:03.912
And last night when we had the move of God, Max, who is an Arab-American now—he got radically saved—was a Palestinian, right?

00:15:03.913 --> 00:15:13.822
Is that right? He saw Jesus walking around in the auditorium, and I knew it was authentic because of the way he said it.

00:15:13.823 --> 00:15:23.457
Now, not every vision do I believe; when somebody says they're seeing things, I just go, 'Whatever.'But this man I know is authentic.

00:15:23.457 --> 00:15:29.374
His name is Max, and he said he saw Jesus walking around last night in the service.

00:15:29.375 --> 00:15:36.359
But you could feel it. You could feel the tangible presence of God last night.

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:44.819
Diana and I were in there. We could see the mist. And, like I said, I don't try to get all hyper-spiritual about stuff.

00:15:44.820 --> 00:15:48.990
If it's there, it's there. If it's not, it's not. And it was there. It was the same.

00:15:48.991 --> 00:15:56.221
Diana said it wasn't as thick as what we saw in the tent last year at this meeting when we went to the mountain and we went out there.

00:15:56.222 --> 00:16:02.882
They have the fish fry and all the things that are on Monday, and that's when the Holy Spirit was so strong.

00:16:02.883 --> 00:16:09.839
We even saw it; it was so thick you couldn't see through it—the glory cloud.

00:16:09.840 --> 00:16:18.019
Last night, we started worshiping, and the glory of the Lord came in, and it was tangible.

00:16:18.020 --> 00:16:26.034
Now, I didn't see Jesus, but Max did, and I think another man. Right.

00:16:26.035 --> 00:16:34.079
So, he was walking around the aisles examining the troops, examining his children.

00:16:34.080 --> 00:16:39.912
And when we were up there and they were worshiping, they started singing the song.

00:16:39.913 --> 00:16:55.199
And she started singing, and the glory of the Lord came into the building, and, ladies and gentlemen, I kid you not, you could see a mist in the atmosphere.

00:16:55.200 --> 00:17:10.869
There was a heavy dew; you could feel it. Now, I don't know if everybody could see it, but there were quite a few that said they did, and you could feel the presence—the tangible presence of God. And I'm all about it.

00:17:10.870 --> 00:17:27.006
I told Sister Billie today, I said, 'I could park myself in a meeting like that and never leave.'People were—she told everybody they could go home because it was already so late, and people didn't want to leave.

00:17:27.007 --> 00:17:38.938
Some of them left, which I think—they missed out big time. The people who left, I just don't, honest to goodness, I don't know how you can leave a service and say, 'Well, I'm going home to go to bed.'What else is there to stay up for?

00:17:38.939 --> 00:17:44.679
If God's there and the glory cloud's there, you couldn't pay me a million dollars to want to leave that.

00:17:44.680 --> 00:17:53.959
I mean, seriously, the tangible presence of God is in the building, folks, and you want to go lay on your pillow?

00:17:53.960 --> 00:18:01.609
Forget it. I mean, there ain't nothing in this world—that's all that I'm living for is the presence and the glory.

00:18:01.610 --> 00:18:08.999
So, we could feel it. You could feel the tangible presence, and you could feel the weightiness of his presence.

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:20.439
But like I said, Max was blessed with the vision of it, to see the Lord Jesus walking around looking at people.

00:18:20.440 --> 00:18:27.395
Some people were experiencing angels and things like that, but it was more that didn't than did.

00:18:27.396 --> 00:18:33.843
But the glory, everybody—I think you would have to be spiritually dead not to feel it.

00:18:33.844 --> 00:18:38.839
I mean seriously, the atmosphere was tangible—the presence of God.

00:18:38.840 --> 00:18:49.314
I'm so grateful, so thankful to experience the glory, so grateful. There is nothing like it, there's nothing like it.

00:18:49.315 --> 00:18:57.945
And for all the people who traveled—they had people from, like I said, South Korea, they had people from China, they had people from all over the globe.

00:18:57.946 --> 00:19:04.876
They brought them up today and were talking about it. It was so cool to see so many people came from so many different places.

00:19:04.877 --> 00:19:08.079
And the people from Switzerland. Two different people from Switzerland.

00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:21.652
And I didn't realize there are that many different dialects in Switzerland.

00:19:21.653 --> 00:19:30.839
German, Italian, French—three different languages in different sectors. I didn't realize that.

00:19:30.840 --> 00:19:35.751
So we had the French represented here, and we had the Germans, from what I understood.

00:19:35.752 --> 00:19:45.306
So I thought, 'Well, praise God.'But really, really beautiful, really beautiful what the Lord is doing, but I'm expecting even more.

00:19:45.307 --> 00:19:57.077
You know, I know there's more. I know there's more. And I believe we are just entering in—first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:19:57.078 --> 00:20:03.436
I believe for this revival that we're experiencing, I believe we're just entering into it.

00:20:03.437 --> 00:20:11.697
You can just barely see that blade coming up out of the ground for what's about to happen. It's just barely peeking through.

00:20:11.698 --> 00:20:19.399
You know, when you just get that seed, that little hatchling, the little seed is just barely poking itself through the soil.

00:20:19.400 --> 00:20:23.854
And I believe even like, you know, some people are talking about a turning point and all this stuff.

00:20:23.855 --> 00:20:29.379
Yes, but there's something so much more coming on the edge of time.

00:20:29.380 --> 00:20:33.654
All the stuff that's happening, folks, I'm telling you, we are right there.

00:20:33.655 --> 00:20:45.766
I even told Pastor Chip, one of the pastors, I told him, 'We've got to stop saying it's coming and start saying it's here.'And he said that's exactly what the Lord was telling him.

00:20:45.767 --> 00:20:51.294
But I believe when we start saying it's here, the glory is here.

00:20:51.295 --> 00:20:56.486
The glory and the manifested presence of the Lord is here. It's not coming.

00:20:56.487 --> 00:21:04.460
We're not going to experience it later on. Because if it's always coming, something is coming all the time.

00:21:04.461 --> 00:21:12.752
But I started thinking, get the mindset of expectation for the manifestation now. Why is it always tomorrow?

00:21:12.753 --> 00:21:17.345
It's like believing God always for tomorrow for your deliverance, for your marriage to get better.

00:21:17.346 --> 00:21:23.815
'Well, tomorrow's going to get better.'Why not now? Why not have your expiration date to what you're believing for now?

00:21:23.816 --> 00:21:30.239
Why not believe for the exceedingly abundantly above all that you would ask or think now?

00:21:30.240 --> 00:21:34.195
So, I'm believing for it tonight. I'm believing for it tomorrow. I'm believing right now.

00:21:34.196 --> 00:21:44.694
Let's just always stay in that constant state of being, in that constant state of believing that you receive it when you come together and you fellowship like that.

00:21:44.695 --> 00:21:50.319
And I thought, you know, it's a pull. You pull it. You can pull it.

00:21:50.320 --> 00:22:10.136
And it was cool because Sister Lynn was talking about praying for North Korea today and getting over in those rivers and praying, because, you know, she said it was interesting—I love her illustrations—she was talking about how there's no pictures, there's really no information about North Korea because it's so closed off.

00:22:10.137 --> 00:22:20.825
It's a wall. But as you pray into something, she said she takes her notebook and she writes everything about North Korea, what she's getting about that in prayer.

00:22:20.826 --> 00:22:29.837
And after a while, she has notebooks full, a prayer journal of everything that she has gotten from the Holy Spirit concerning North Korea.

00:22:29.838 --> 00:23:01.188
So I have gotten all this stuff about North Korea and praying into that, about what the Lord has told us—that He was going to remove a tyrant, that He was going to remove Kim Jong-un, and that his days were numbered, that his sister's days were numbered, that God was going to give North Korea a window of opportunity for a major outpouring of the Spirit of God, and that there would be a great harvest of souls in the days to come concerning North Korea and South Korea and China and basically all of Asia.

00:23:01.189 --> 00:23:08.390
And He said, 'We're going to have a major move of God in Asia.'So that's what we're believing for.

00:23:08.391 --> 00:23:15.162
He said, 'I have not forgotten my Asians. I have not forgotten the Asians.

00:23:15.163 --> 00:23:32.722
They have felt that they have been forgotten.'But the Lord said, 'Brandon, I have not forgotten my Asians, and there is going to be the greatest harvest of souls that they've ever experienced, ever in all of time, that Asia will have a move of God.'And that's what we're believing for.

00:23:32.723 --> 00:23:47.959
So, going back to—I don't want to get sidetracked—going back to the Tomahawks now, President Trump right now is negotiating and talking about sending some long-range missiles into there, trying to stiff-arm Putin.

00:23:47.960 --> 00:23:58.731
And I said, 'Don't poke the bear.'Remember, every single thing we're getting: don't poke the bear, don't send these long-range missiles.

00:23:58.732 --> 00:24:11.593
So, as we're praying into that, I believe we can stop some of that to delay it and make it not happen, because this is going to be very bad for Poland and Romania and some of these other nations.

00:24:11.594 --> 00:24:32.734
But as we see the enemy within the Red Dawn experience, the Lord said, 'We must pray for America because of what I saw yesterday concerning the major building that was on fire at the top.'And He said, 'This is the distraction from the main thing.

00:24:32.735 --> 00:25:04.758
This building was to attract the firefighters, the emergency crew responders, from the main event.'And I saw tripwires in buildings that were booby-trapped, that when the firefighters walked in, it was over—that they were rigged for a catastrophic event on purpose to delay and to cause a distraction from what they're trying to do over at another place.

00:25:04.759 --> 00:25:10.042
Does that make sense, what I'm trying to tell y'all? It was a deterrent. That's a good word, a deterrent.

00:25:10.043 --> 00:25:16.639
So, that's what we're going to pray into a little bit more today in this little bit of time that we have left here.

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:21.407
So, I hope I gave you a little bit of something to get you excited. It's time, folks.

00:25:21.408 --> 00:25:31.832
